  <condition>Papillary Microcarcinoma</condition>
  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Papillary Microcarcinoma</arm_group_label>
    <description>This clinical trial protocol describes implementation of a prospective observation protocol to standardize data collection and obtain permission to collect samples of PMC tumors in a cohort of PMC patients being followed with active surveillance. This will allow PMC tumors to be accurately classified as either stable or progressive over time and used for comprehensive molecular profiling if surgical removal is required during follow-up</description>
  </arm_group>
